<Layout title="How to Brief and Communicate With Your Solicitor When Selling in Brisbane 2026 | Daniel Gierach Property" description="A practical guide for Brisbane property sellers on what to give your solicitor, when to engage them, the communication cadence that works, and how to keep the contract phase clean from briefing through settlement." schema={faqSchema}>

<article style="background:var(--color-surface-0);min-height:100vh;">

  <!-- Hero -->
  <div style="background:#0a0806;padding:8rem 0 3rem;">
    <div class="max-w-[780px] mx-auto px-8">
